=> Image compression

 - jpeg optimizer, tiny PNG, Optimizilla
  <picture>
    <source srcset="photo.avif" type="image/avif"></source> //avif format is the fast 
    <img src="photo.jpg alt="Photo"> ////fallback image
  </picture>
  this picutre tag will check for the first source to be available if not last img will be shown.
- Device Pixel Ratio
  window.devicePixelRatio
  <img srcset="baby-s.jpg 300w baby-m.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 2420em) 2000px" />

- Adaptive media loading
  - navigator.connector.saveData
  - navigator.deviceMemory
  - navigator.hardwareConcurrency

- CSS sprites
  Images are clubbed together in a virutal grid
